{"questionId":"28026","questionHtml":"<p>Show that the characteristic polynomial of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">T</mi></math>&nbsp;is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1363</mn><msup><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>1263</mn><mi>λ</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>write their matrix with <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>λ</mi></math> subtracted from the leading diagonal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>equate determinant to zero&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>det</mtext><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>29</mn></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mi>λ</mi><mo>&nbsp;</mo></mtd><mtd><mfrac><mn>31</mn><mn>47</mn></mfrac></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mfrac><mn>12</mn><mn>29</mn></mfrac><mo>&nbsp;</mo></mtd><mtd><mfrac><mn>16</mn><mn>47</mn></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mi>λ</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>29</mn></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mi>λ</mi></mrow></mfenced><mfenced><mrow><mfrac><mn>16</mn><mn>47</mn></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mi>λ</mi></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>12</mn><mn>29</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>31</mn><mn>47</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>correct intermediate step</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1363</mn><msup><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>1263</mn><mi>λ</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>AG</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Do not award <em><strong>A1</strong> </em>if there is no intermediate step leading from determinant to given answer.&nbsp;<br>Solving&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">T</mi><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mi>λ</mi><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math>&nbsp;for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>y</mi></math> may be seen and is a valid alternative method.&nbsp;<br>Accept working in the form&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>det</mtext><mfenced><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mi>I</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>T</mi></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"28026","referenceCode":"22N.3.AHL.TZ0.1g.i","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Show that the characteristic polynomial of T is 1363λ2-1263λ-100=0.","paper":"3","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"g.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","AHL 4.15—Central limit theorem"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}